t: "To Allah Ë¹aloneËº belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is on the earth. Indeed, We have commanded those given the Scripture before you, as well as you, to be mindful of Allah. But if you disobey, then Ë¹know thatËº to Allah belongs whatever is in the heavens and the earth. And Allah is Self-Sufficient, Praiseworthy"